org.hkijena.jipipe.api.nodes

Class JIPipeMergingDataBatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.nodes.JIPipeMergingDataBatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<JIPipeMergingDataBatch>

    public class JIPipeMergingDataBatch
extends Object
implements Comparable<JIPipeMergingDataBatch>
    Wraps a set of input and output slots that belong together. This is a less restricted variant of JIPipeDataBatch used by JIPipeMergingAlgorithm
